The issue happens where there are no bindings, but only a named autowiring alias.
This "else" block should look for a `Target` attribute:
https://github.com/symfony/symfony/blob/ca27974f5138120a43a874aa5f21a808ee8ce91c/src/Symfony/Component/HttpKernel/DependencyInjection/RegisterControllerArgumentLocatorsPass.php#L193-L196

Please target 5.4 as this is a bugfix IMHO.

